{"tid":1576132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遊行]點解我地咁多人 唔搞一次新屋嶺遊行","createTime":"2019-09-17T06:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T09:14:26.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29e55a1fde7ad97ffbc7ba1f3110a6a036f46580","tid":1576132,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母! 核彈都同你割! </span><br />\n<br />\n攪送頭遊行?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n研究左地形未? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警等你集晒係門口,就兵分兩路斷道,公安落埋來拉你上去都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時是x蛋公布話拉左100人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男既直接拉去棄屍都搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n女既直接送上支那做雞都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山? 斷背山呀?</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5nXwPM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5nXwPM.png&h=f166bc8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b8f85e03007ce2f6461dd2b1d46781f05e61eec","tid":1576132,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"a7eeace05ac5eadc7a505b0e12ea149c84742cf1","tid":1576132,"uid":54373,"like":0,"